            <description><![CDATA[【[机智]<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%88%AC%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%BF%83%E8%A1%80%E7%AE%A1%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%88%AC%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%BF%83%E8%A1%80%E7%AE%A1%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#爬楼梯有助降低心血管疾病风险#</span></a> 今晚都给我爬！】爬楼梯是一种低成本、便捷的运动方式，每天爬5层（一层10阶）以上楼梯的人，患动脉粥样硬化性心血管疾病的风险降低约20%<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[拳头]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_quantou-81f684d5ed.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 好消息：爬过多了可能适得其反<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4982627967369287" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1gy1hl5c1nbv5cj20k00qoaig.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dFlJY2nYlx08bcI9vJrO01041200dkcF0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1703590925&amp;ssig=%2FFfQPOo69r&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/y7Jc4o4clx08bcI9TqIE01041200727g0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1703590925&amp;ssig=GXRxTZPJ48&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/v4ZAepmalx08bcI9juFO010412003O0O0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1703590925&amp;ssig=8OpWX350AW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4982627967369287" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
